2n arrays. The algorithm repeats this step until there is only one
length-kn sorted array. What is the running time of this procedure,
as a function of k and n, ignoring constant factors and lower-order
terms?

a. n log k
b. nk
c. nk log k
d. nk log n
e. nk^2
f. n^2k

answer:
